data.description: DON'T MISS OUT ON THIS ONE!!! This home was built in 2007 and has a lot to offer. Outside you will love to sit under the covered porch while . Inyou drink your morning coffee.  Inside there is plenty of space in this three bedroom and two bath home. The large living room offers laminated flooring with large windows letting in lots of natural light. Right next to it you have a nice eat in kitchen. This home also offers a primary suite. Fridge stays.  Lots of additional parking in the back of the house. Call today to make your personal appointment before it's to late!!
